This paper proposes a novel multimodal segmentation framework for medical images, specifically for brain tumor segmentation. The approach involves feature disentanglement and gated fusion to handle missing modalities. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
